Name: Cool Headed
About the game: Cool Headed is a puzzle casual-programming game. Combine and use your bots to reach the objective! How to play? Pick a level on the overworld Compose your team Give orders, tweak the timings Deploy! Try again... Win by having one bot reaching the objective. Will you have the heart to sacrifice the rest of the team? Features more then 110 level of progressive difficulty bots with diverse abilities no time pressure and unlimited tries lots of secrets to uncover Good luck!
